data.description: Amazing Stonebrair…Calera's charming sidewalk community. One-level, 3 bed 2 bath home boasts welcoming covered-porch entry. Expansive great doom with high ceilings, crown molding throughout wall of windows offering picturesque view of wooded tree sanctuary. Cozy kitchen features light-filled breakfast nook next to covered patio & wooded yard. Large master suite offers volume trey ceiling & large walk-in closet. Master bath features dual vanities, separate shower & garden tub. 2 additional main-level bedrooms share full bath. Convenient walk-up attic with lots of storage or can be easily converted to a finished bonus room. Welcome Home! 2012 New Back door screened security door; 2017 New HVAC system; 2021 New Roof and Vents; 2021 New Faucets in both baths
